Download cuda 9.1

Downgrade kernel version:
https://devtalk.nvidia.com/default/topic/1028566/cuda-setup-and-installation/cuda-9-1-install-fail-with-ubuntu-16-04-kernel-version-4-13-0-26/

Switch off of Nvidia drivers in GUI

Exit x:
ctrl+alt+f1
*systemd service lightroomdm stop
sudo init 3

Run cuda installer
